title: Farha (2021)
name: Farha (2021)

trailer.name: Official Trailer
trailer.description: Farha (2021) In 1948 Palestine, 14-year-old Farha dreams of pursuing an education beyond her village. Just as her father agrees to let her delay marriage and attend a city school, their peaceful life shatters. Israeli forces arrive, displacing villagers and forcing Farha's family to flee. To protect Farha, her father hides her in a small, concealed pantry within their home. Trapped in darkness, she listens to the escalating violence outside, relying on scraps of information from the occasional visitor. Days turn into weeks as Farha grapples with fear, loneliness, and the uncertainty of her future. Through the sounds and smells filtering through the pantry door, Farha witnesses the destruction of her village and the trauma inflicted on her community. This confined perspective becomes a powerful lens through which the film portrays the devastating impact of the Nakba on ordinary lives. Farha is a poignant coming-of-age story that delves into themes of resilience, hope, and the enduring power of memory in the face of displacement and loss.

Refusing to accept the accusations against his wife, Amin embarks on a personal quest to uncover the truth. The film skillfully weaves a suspenseful thriller with a profound exploration of identity, betrayal, and the profound human cost of political violence. Amin's investigation takes him on a dangerous journey into the heart of the Israeli-Palestinian conflict, where he confronts uncomfortable truths about Siham, their relationship, and the broader political realities shaping their lives.

trailer.description: Suka (2023):  sebuah film aksi drama yang lahir dari industri perfilman Australia, disutradarai oleh Heidi Lee Douglas dan ditulis oleh Tsu Shan Chambers serta Lily Cheng. Dibintangi oleh Paul W. He, Jenny Wu, Grace Huang, Ethan Browne, Tsu Shan Chambers, Loretta Kung, dan Tony Goh, film ini memasuki layar pada 23 September 2023. Ceritanya berlatar di Western Sydney, di mana dua keluarga kriminal, Dawood dan Yang, bersaing sengit untuk meraih kekuasaan. Matriark Dawood, Wasiya (Jenny Wu), menjadi pusat konflik dalam kisah ini, dengan tekad kuat untuk menghentikan keluarga saingannya, Yang, yang dipimpin oleh Jun (Tony Goh). Ketegangan semakin memuncak ketika Wasiya mengetahui bahwa Jun telah membunuh suaminya ketika dia sedang hamil.
